nl_command: whenever 100kV Transmission Line occurs CPCC Kratt must occur at the very next time instant
ltl: G i 100kv_transmission_line X cpcc_kratt

nl_command: CPCC Advanced Technology Center should happen immediately in the next time step as soon as CPCC Worrell is observed
ltl: G i cpcc_worrell X cpcc_advanced_technology_center

nl_command: CPCC Advanced Technology Center should happen immediately in the next time step as soon as CPCC Tate Tower is observed
ltl: G i cpcc_tate_tower X cpcc_advanced_technology_center

ltl: G i cpcc_kratt X gloria_victus_monument

nl_command: if you see CPCC Advanced Technology Center then go to CPCC Health Careers at the very next time step
ltl: G i cpcc_advanced_technology_center X cpcc_health_careers

ltl: G i independence_park X cpcc_giles_science_center

nl_command: always the response to CPCC Citizens Center is CPCC Overcash - Arts Wing in the next time step
ltl: G i cpcc_citizens_center X cpcc_overcash_-_arts_wing

nl_command: go to Gloria Victus Monument in the very next time instant whenever you see CPCC Central High
ltl: G i cpcc_central_high X gloria_victus_monument

nl_command: always if you observe Central Piedmont Community College proceed to reach CPCC Advanced Technology Center at the very next time instant
ltl: G i central_piedmont_community_college X cpcc_advanced_technology_center

nl_command: always if you observe CPCC Overcash - Arts Wing proceed to reach CPCC Overcash at the very next time instant
ltl: G i cpcc_overcash_-_arts_wing X cpcc_overcash

nl_command: whenever you observe Independence Park proceed to go to reach CPCC Library at the next time instant
ltl: G i independence_park X cpcc_library

ltl: G i little_sugar_creek X cpcc_faculty/theatre_parking
